data.name: lblInstructions.Text
data.value:
To play you just press Space, this fires the ball, to pause press esc
You use W and S as player 1 and up and down arrow for player 2
You have to get the ball past the other player as much as possible in 5 minutes.
When you score, you will get a random amount of points. This increases difficulty
When the timer hits both 200 and 100, more paddels appear in the middle and move, to increase difficulty of the game progressively.
There are 4 randomly appearing powerups that may help or hinder you.
The Crack Powerup will display a big crack in the middle of the screen which makes it hard to see the ball for 30 seconds.
The Grow powerup will make the paddle of whoever hit the ball last get bigger, making it easier to hit the ball for 30 seconds
The Slow powerup will make the ball very slow for 30 seconds making it easier for both players.
The Reverse powerup will switch the controls of the player who hit the ball last causing disorientation for 30 Seconds
At the end of the game you will know if you or the other player beat the high score and who won.
